{"tid":930068,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"特斯拉上海「超級工廠」　搶先2019下半年部分投產","createTime":"2018-12-06T04:47:01.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-06T06:54:45.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ab18fbfbff14a4186242df72a936698a1fe10949","tid":930068,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T04:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3511/d3511531.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3511%2Fd3511531.jpg&h=89fcc5be&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲▼馬斯克在離開中國前發了與特斯拉中國同事在紫光閣的合影。（圖／翻攝自Elon Musk推特）<br />\n▲馬斯克今年7月初訪華，敲定在上海的投資案。（圖／翻攝自Elon Musk推特）<br />\n<br />\n記者陳政錄／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n美國電動車大廠特斯拉（Tesla）正在加速上海「超級工廠」的投產腳步，據陸媒報導，上海市長應勇昨日調研上海重大投資項目時，位於臨港的特斯拉生產基地即將開工建設，預計明年下半年部分投產，較原定時程大幅提前。<br />\n<br />\n為規避關稅壁壘、擴大中國市場布局，特斯拉CEO馬斯克今年七月初訪華時，敲定在中國的投資案，於臨近洋山深水港的臨港產業區，獨資建設集研發、 製造、銷售等功能於一體的特斯拉超級工廠（Gigafactory 3），原定2020年起陸續投產，規畫年產50萬輛純電動整車<br />\n<br />\n▲▼洋山深水港四期。（圖／記者陳政錄攝）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3653/d3653277.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3653%2Fd3653277.jpg&h=6ac1a954&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲臨港區接近上海洋山深水港，對外貿易便利。（圖／記者陳政錄攝）<br />\n<br />\n今年10月17日，官方資訊披露，特斯拉與上海市規劃和國土資源管理局，正式簽訂土地出讓合約，以9.73億元人民幣的合約金額，取得86萬4885平方公尺的工業用地，代表特斯拉的上海「超級工廠」在臨港完成了實質落地。<br />\n<br />\n據《解放日報》報導，上海市長應勇5日調研上海市重大投資項目建設情況時，特斯拉中國區負責人透露，目前項目已基本完成土地平整，即將開工建設，預計明年下半年部分投產。他說，將在確保生產安全和工程質量的前提下，加快推進工廠建設。<br />\n<br />\n▲▼網友推特問Model 3何時在台上市　馬斯克親回：2019中期。（圖／翻攝自Tesla）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3724/d3724013.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3724%2Fd3724013.jpg&h=0f0fdde7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲特斯拉上海工廠最快2019年上半年投產。（圖／翻攝自Tesla）<br />\n<br />\n今年8月，特斯拉官網上發布上海工廠第一批員工的資訊，包括EPC工程總監、政府事務項目經理、施工經理、土木工程師等等，據業內人士指出，挖角薪資最多將近3倍。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181206/1324213.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20181206%2F1324213.htm&d=25lWIakmnjXfrruxfuQJpVeK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=d215a360\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20181206/1324213.htm</a>"},{"pid":"d2d9ebb0729225b0c39190f28b8cda44e66f0fea","tid":930068,"uid":2429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:00:19.000Z","msg":"習武帝又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cfb3ff69d68c9f1d91e07511275a1c9fe8e0017","tid":930068,"uid":3704,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:18:33.000Z","msg":"比XX: 多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdfb127580e1a1489122bcf51b89e5b134be9f13","tid":930068,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:19:50.000Z","msg":"大陸佬有錢都買made in usa啦on9"},{"pid":"681bde847259439775a5e1a6452ad03af69e82f4","tid":930068,"uid":1989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cdfb127580e1a1489122bcf51b89e5b134be9f13","tid":930068,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:19:50.000Z","msg":"大陸佬有錢都買made in usa啦on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:26:14.000Z","msg":"Made in china賣香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10c4b9e4e0dee03e49cf92f9a36c62c147bfad1b","tid":930068,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:45:34.000Z","msg":"copy copy copy <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba3a5d3d57a50526b6bd320fdefb4d30a49754d7","tid":930068,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T05:53:06.000Z","msg":"一陣俾支那偷晒技術踢走"},{"pid":"e873279da749cf9f1d1a1f1120ea3d62fc425aa6","tid":930068,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-06T06:27:21.000Z","msg":"「邪惡太了解善良，而善良的人，毫不了解邪惡」（Evil knows of the good, but good does not know of evil）"},{"pid":"c6a993a